Bug ID:002
Title: 3.Profile phone works with"-" ,"+" and other symbols.
Description: Adding your phone number works with "-" at the beggining.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on Hello,(Username)!
Step 4 : Add your phone number with "-" at the beggining.
Step 5 : Click the "Save" button.
Step 6 : Check the confirmation message.


Expected Result:
After filling the Phone number field with a "-" you should get the "The Phone number field is not a valid phone number." message.
It should only work with the symbol "+" infront.

Actual Result:
After filling the Phone number field with a "-" you get "Your profile has been updated".

Severity:
Low

Priority:
Low

Additional Information:
This works with "(",")","." and "-" but does not work with other symbols like "@","#".

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
